OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772093097
OL,3,CPaul Mescal spotted in Liverpool
OL,4,Cfilming for new four-part Beatles
OL,5,Cbiopics
OL,7,FHollywood stars including Paul Mescal
OL,8,Fhave been spotted filming what is
OL,9,Fbelieved to be the new series of The
OL,10,FBeatles biopics.
OL,12,FCameras were seen outside the former
OL,13,Fhome of John Lennon, on Menlove
OL,14,FAvenue, in Woolton, Liverpool, as the
OL,15,Fstreet was taken back in time for the
OL,16,Fseries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
