CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772093097
OL,3,CPaul Mescal spotted in Liverpool
OL,4,Cfilming for new four-part Beatles
OL,5,Cbiopics
OL,7,FCrews are expected to remain in
OL,8,FWoolton for the duration of the week,
OL,9,Fwhere screens had been erected to
OL,10,Fblock passers by getting a peak at
OL,11,Fwhat was being filmed.
OL,13,FMore commonly known as Mendips, John
OL,14,Flived at the address with his aunt
OL,15,FMimi until 1963.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
