PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772093097
OL,3,CPaul Mescal spotted in Liverpool
OL,4,Cfilming for new four-part Beatles
OL,5,Cbiopics
OL,7,FThe series of films, which are
OL,8,Fcurrently in production, are slated to
OL,9,Fbe released in 2028 and will star Paul
OL,10,FMescal as Sir Paul McCartney, Barry
OL,11,FKeoghan as Sir Ringo Starr, Harris
OL,12,FDickinson as John Lennon and Joseph
OL,13,FQuinn as George Harrison.
OL,15,FPaul Mescal could be seen as Sir Paul
OL,16,FMcCartney on set, with Leanne Best
OL,17,Fplaying Aunt Mimi as she hung out the
OL,18,Fwindow of Mendips.
OL,20,FA road sign states City Road will also
OL,21,Fbe closed until 1am on 28 February.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
